race.comment: DRAGONNE ROUGE (3) has contested two Listed races since returning from a spell and has settled too far back to be a force on either occasion. Won the Listed Calaway Gal over this course and distance third-up last prep. Only needs to find that sort of form to be taking this out. MRS GOLDBERG (8) surprised a few pundits when she led all the way and held out subsequent winner Fabulantes over this distance at the Sunshine Coast last time out. Has only raced three times so there is plenty more in the locker. BRUTAL MISS (6) started favourite in the MRS GOLDBERG race last start but settled back and was never in the hunt. Lines up for just the third time so deserves another chance. HERMAN SAID (7) heads north after some good runs at Newcastle where he has been ridden positively. Consider.
